Interface ContestantCloning

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    ContestantsBenchClientProxy, PlaygroundClientProxy

    public interface ContestantCloning
    Contestant cloning.

    It specifies his own attributes. Implementation of a client-server model of type 2 (server replication). Communication is based on a communication channel under the TCP protocol.
